{
  "stem": "21437.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some people who were older than I was, they said, if they will let me bleed, then I will survive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't consciously fight for my survival at any stage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was too young, apparently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I think that, in a passive way, or in a-- what-- what was my weapon?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is that I somehow could respond to the kindness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's unbelievable that today you hear sometimes that people don't get on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't really believe that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember once that you stood in the queue for that little bit of water, for the little bit of bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they called you out, you ran out and you stood wherever you were-- wherever was the line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was never any pushing or never any pulling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we saw occasionally-- when we had this bit of a bread-- I just heard recently-- somebody who's my second cousin described how she had in her-- this mattress that supposedly to be a mattress.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hid those photos that I showed you before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she hid her little potions of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were molded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She didn't eat them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because she felt that, if later on, suddenly she will have all this enormous amount of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was in her imagination.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That she will devour all of this bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this will-- this will, you know-- this will let her survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she didn't eat this bread, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She hid it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like we saw the [INAUDIBLE]-- if we had-- sometimes, some people, when they got a bit of bread-- [GASP] you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A second later, it was nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the whole day, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some people waited with it for the last minute.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
